We love watching them as a family and talking about the morals and values and other life lessons learned as well as delving into the characters themselves.  I loved this series as a girl and am grateful they are here for my boys to enjoy now.  These are wonderful gifts for a family.

As I was feared the great thanksgiving special LITTLE HOUSE YEARS which was broadcasted between episodes 9 and 10 of season 6 is still missing an official dvd release and it's also not included in this set.
 I really don't get it. there were 5 tv specials. the pilot the little house years and the three post telefilms.
 all were released except this season 6 tv special.
 why they ignored this ?
 this is an integral part of the series as it's about nostalgia showing the past years the family had in a 3 hour tv movie with great credits.
 I hoped they would include this here but I was wrong.
 for LHOTP fans this is a major flaw. WE WANT THIS SPECIAL IN DVD FOR CHRIST SAKE.

Purchased this as a gift.  I've not watched this personally, so I can not comment on the program itself.  However I wanted to point out that this collection arrived with no slip cover that came with all the other seasons I had also purchased as gifts.  The recipients collection of all the other seasons which were purchase at box stores had slip covers.  So I had to return it and purchase from a mega store to complete the collection.  If this is something you don't care about then it won't be a problem for you.  Amazon continues to drop the ball on DVDs and CDs.

Another season added to my larder.  Real nice quality and great packaging.  Why all the hoopla about the packaging?  Because when they first released the series on DVD, it was all flash.  A whole lot of plasticc and nothing more.  Now two seasons of the newly released series equal one in terms of how much room they take up.  That's always a nice deal if you get what you want and save space too.
